Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.22,0:00:18.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Now you just have to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.26,0:00:24.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,These words lured men to the Grand Line in pursuit of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.53,0:00:26.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,dreams greater than they'd ever dared to imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.11,0:00:29.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,This is the time known as the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.49,0:00:33.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Come aboard and bring along all your hopes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.09,0:00:35.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,and dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.03,0:00:39.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Together we will find everything that we're looking
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.87,0:00:41.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,for.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.95,0:00:42.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.03,0:00:52.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,The compass left behind, it'll only slow us down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.01,0:00:56.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Your Heart will be your guide, raise the sails
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.10,0:00:58.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,and take the helm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:04.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,That legendary place that the end of the map reveals
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.84,0:01:10.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Is only legendary until someone proves it real.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.50,0:01:14.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Through it all, through all the troubled times,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.60,0:01:17.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,through the heartache and through the pain, know that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.20,0:01:21.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I will be there to stand by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.35,0:01:24.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Just like I know you'll stand by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.99,0:01:29.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,So come aboard and bring along all your hopes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.81,0:01:31.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,and dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.77,0:01:35.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Together we will find everything that we're looking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.57,0:01:37.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,for.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:40.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,There's always room for you If you want to be my friend
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.49,0:01:42.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We are, we are on the cruise We are
