Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.05,0:01:57.68,Title-207-,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(561,1022)\c&HE7E6E6&\bord0\4a&HFF&}The Silent Man
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.04,0:02:04.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Brutton woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.26,0:02:08.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,How dare you try to make a fool of the great Captain Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.12,0:02:12.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Insulting me for having the blood of a pirate?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.05,0:02:14.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Please, you don't have to do this, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.54,0:02:37.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Klahadore?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.84,0:02:40.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Klahadore, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.74,0:02:42.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hello, Klahadore? 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:45.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.45,0:02:47.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.13,0:02:49.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.81,0:02:51.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:52.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.97,0:02:53.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Please wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.15,0:02:54.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.43,0:02:56.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Please don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.93,0:02:58.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.29,0:03:00.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.69,0:03:01.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I was worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.29,0:03:03.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.59,0:03:09.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You have to tell me who did this to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.78,0:03:11.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Klawhador.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.06,0:03:12.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,That's who.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.26,0:03:14.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He attacked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:17.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He's a. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:19.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He's a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.48,0:03:21.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He's never been anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.81,0:03:23.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,How could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.13,0:03:28.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He got close to you just so he could steal your Fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:30.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,That's all he ever wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:48.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,And what Usopp spoke about yesterday was the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.32,0:03:51.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.28,0:03:53.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,And that's what is most tragic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.62,0:03:56.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,When he learned the truth, he tried his hardest to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.97,0:03:58.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,get us to hear him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.41,0:04:01.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,But we we're all too shallow-minded, too confident in
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.41,0:04:03.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,the closed-off world we've lived in for
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.41,0:04:05.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,so long to listen to a single word.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:07.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:08.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Run, Kaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.53,0:04:09.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,They're going to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.74,0:04:13.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I promise this will all make sense tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.45,0:04:19.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,In our blind protection of the villain in our midst,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.68,0:04:22.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,we drove away the one brave lad whose desperate
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:26.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,resolve he enacted for the sake and safety of every
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:29.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,person of this village, including you and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.68,0:04:32.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Someone help!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.53,0:04:33.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mary needs help!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.18,0:04:34.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,No, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.22,0:04:36.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It's of no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:41.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,The entire staff is on leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.29,0:04:43.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,No one has been here since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.13,0:04:44.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:45.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Then I just. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.15,0:04:46.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'll find. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:49.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You cannot let yourself get flustered, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.95,0:04:51.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We know the attack has yet to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:55.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,So be calm, and think clearly about what it is you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.47,0:04:56.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Have to do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.05,0:05:01.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Because if Klawhador is the thief we understand him
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.83,0:05:04.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,to be, and his goal is your fortune and your mansion,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.33,0:05:06.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,then by all means, let him have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.73,0:05:09.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,None of this is worth sacrificing your life over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:12.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.39,0:05:16.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It's a cruel truth, but you are the only one who can
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:18.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,stop Klawhador now, Kaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.68,0:05:21.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.98,0:05:25.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I know this is not your\Nburden, but still, I must ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.36,0:05:28.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yes, I understand, and I will do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.06,0:05:31.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,This isn't a situation I can run away from.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.21,0:05:34.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I know what consequences I face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:37.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I will find Klawhador and I will finish this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.12,0:05:42.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:44.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You saw Klawhador heading to the shore?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:48.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and he had this weird, scary look on his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:51.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Carrot, would you wake up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.27,0:05:55.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Come on, it's way too early for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.81,0:05:57.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,This is no time for laziness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:05:59.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Horrible things could be happening right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.26,0:06:05.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I still think the pirates are going to attack soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:07.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I know our Captain said that was a lie,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.98,0:06:09.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,but I think he was the one that was lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.68,0:06:12.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're probably right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.95,0:06:13.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It was weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.67,0:06:14.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He seemed off yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:16.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,The Captain wasn't his usual self.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.99,0:06:17.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It's Kaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.97,0:06:18.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,She's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:32.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Looks like something's got her really bothered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.26,0:06:36.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yeah, walking around outside\Nby yourself doesn't seem right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.78,0:06:37.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Something's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.80,0:06:40.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Something really weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:48.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Come forth, Meowban!
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.14,0:06:53.14,Captions-207-,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.7\fad(478,0)\an8\bord5\fnDFPGiHi-W7-Strp\fscx85\fscy90\pos(720,60)\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(436,478,\1a&H00&)}{Siam\NShip Guard - Funi}Siam\NShip Guard\NBlack Cat Pirates{Polly}
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.14,0:06:53.14,Captions-207-,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.7\fad(478,0)\an8\bord0.5\fnDFPGiHi-W7-Strp\fscx85\fscy90\pos(720,60)\3c&HFAFAFB&\c&HFAFAFB&\1a&HFF&\t(436,478,\1a&H00&)\4a&HFF&}{Siam\NShip Guard - Funi}Siam\NShip Guard\NBlack Cat Pirates{Polly}
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.14,0:06:53.14,Captions-207-,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.7\fad(478,0)\an8\bord0\fnDFPGiHi-W7-Strp\fscx85\fscy90\pos(720,60)\c&HFAFAFB&\4a&HFF&}{Siam\NShip Guard - Funi}Siam\NShip Guard\NBlack Cat Pirates{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:51.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yes, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.85,0:06:53.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Did you call for us?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.31,0:06:56.44,Captions-207-,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.7\fad(478,0)\an2\bord5\fnDFPGiHi-W7-Strp\fscx85\fscy90\pos(720,630)\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(436,478,\1a&H00&)}{Butchie\NShip Guard - Funi}Butchie\NShip Guard\NBlack Cat Pirates{Polly}
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.31,0:06:56.44,Captions-207-,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.7\fad(478,0)\an2\bord0.5\fnDFPGiHi-W7-Strp\fscx85\fscy90\pos(720,630)\3c&HF9F9FA&\c&HF9F9FA&\1a&HFF&\t(436,478,\1a&H00&)\4a&HFF&}{Butchie\NShip Guard - Funi}Butchie\NShip Guard\NBlack Cat Pirates{Polly}
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.31,0:06:56.44,Captions-207-,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.7\fad(478,0)\an2\bord0\fnDFPGiHi-W7-Strp\fscx85\fscy90\pos(720,630)\c&HF9F9FA&\4a&HFF&}{Butchie\NShip Guard - Funi}Butchie\NShip Guard\NBlack Cat Pirates{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:56.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Well, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.95,0:06:57.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Siam!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.05,0:06:58.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,And Butchie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.37,0:07:01.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Together we are the Meowban brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:02.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,At your service.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.31,0:07:09.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Butchie, Siam, we absolutely must get up this hill,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.56,0:07:11.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,but as you can plainly see, our path is blocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:16.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,If you would be so kind as to remove this obstacle immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.42,0:07:17.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:18.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We couldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.56,0:07:19.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He looks too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:20.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Right, Butchie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.55,0:07:22.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, he's strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:24.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Way stronger than us. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:28.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Besides, we just guard the ship, not fight people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.29,0:07:30.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He's got a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.21,0:07:32.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We're really not the guys\Nyou want to send into battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:35.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,So, they're a couple of pansies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:37.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I guess they're not the trump card after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:39.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Siam, just do it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.70,0:07:40.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:41.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He's not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:42.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,And hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:43.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.22,0:07:45.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Just stop yelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.54,0:07:47.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,The guy's crying like a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.04,0:07:48.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What are they doing down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.69,0:07:52.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Of all people, why force that guy into a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:54.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'm going to tear you up with these claws!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.52,0:07:56.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You just wait and see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.06,0:07:58.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'm a vicious killing machine and I'm coming for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:07:59.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You bad people!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.22,0:08:02.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You come any closer and I'll cut you in half!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.34,0:08:04.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'm not joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:05.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.55,0:08:08.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Not likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.89,0:08:14.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Preston
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:15.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:18.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It seems you fell for my little ruse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.81,0:08:21.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed you blocked me, considering what a
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.42,0:08:22.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,brilliant performance I gave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.14,0:08:26.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Don't let the teeny bit of skill you have cause you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.54,0:08:29.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,to underestimate Siam of the Meowban brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.98,0:08:35.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Are you missing something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.18,0:08:36.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Not that I would know anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.92,0:08:39.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.97,0:08:40.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Cat burglar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:43.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Give me my swords back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.67,0:08:44.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Your swords?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.69,0:08:46.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,But you already have a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.05,0:08:47.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,How greedy can you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.23,0:08:52.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Say goodbye, swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:53.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:03.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Now I feel lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:06.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You should take care with other people's things!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:18.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You really have to be faster,\Nbecause I'm agile as a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.82,0:09:25.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Butchie, you're up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.38,0:09:26.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Get in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.34,0:09:27.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sedentia!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:39.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Damn, Butchie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:40.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He got away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:43.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Now he's right there, and I hold him tight this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.55,0:09:44.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Careful, he's strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:47.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Stronger than I thought he'd be, even without all his blades.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:50.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,This is getting worse by the second.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.03,0:09:53.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,If tubby there would have landed on me, I'd have been
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:55.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,pounded into the dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.58,0:09:57.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We'll get him for sure this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:09:58.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You got that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.04,0:10:01.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,One-sword technique's not my forte, fellas,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:01.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,but what the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:05.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Butchie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.44,0:10:07.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Right, Siam, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:19.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.39,0:10:20.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,They got him on the defensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.09,0:10:25.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.41,0:10:27.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,There's no way that Zoro can gain any ground
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.61,0:10:29.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,if he's too busy blocking their attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.55,0:10:30.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'm going to help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:32.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.17,0:10:34.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:42.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,This is our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:49.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to shoot at the bad guys, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:51.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,But I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:53.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It was. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:55.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It was like he moved in front of my shot on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.27,0:10:57.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,But why would he do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:00.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.94,0:11:01.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Don't help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.10,0:11:02.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You want to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:10.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It's just a thought, but maybe it's the two of us who
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:11.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,just got saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.46,0:11:14.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,If you had actually hit one of those guys, they would
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.44,0:11:15.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Have come after us instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.54,0:11:18.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,And we wouldn't have had a chance of holding up
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:19.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,against that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.33,0:11:20.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:23.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,All this time he was worried about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:30.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,If I just had one more sword, I could take these guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.24,0:11:34.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get the swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.65,0:11:36.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,If I can get them back to Zoro, there'll be no way he
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.74,0:11:37.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,can lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.34,0:11:39.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Let me get the swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.66,0:11:41.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Don't push yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.82,0:11:43.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You can barely even stand up on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.49,0:11:45.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:07.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.23,0:12:09.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What do you need swords for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.77,0:12:25.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.53,0:12:26.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.99,0:12:29.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I can explain all of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.24,0:12:37.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,The night has long since passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:41.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,So why is it that you seem to have made no progress
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.33,0:12:42.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,on the plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.81,0:12:43.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:44.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Kuro! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.05,0:12:46.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He'll kill us all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.21,0:12:54.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:12.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.89,0:13:19.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,To think that these brats have held you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.04,0:13:23.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,How the Black Cat Pirates have fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:26.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What have you got to say for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.17,0:13:28.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Djongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.31,0:13:36.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,But, , well, I. . . You said. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:40.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sir, but you said letting the kid go wouldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.51,0:13:41.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,cause any problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:46.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I did say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:48.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What's your point?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.88,0:13:49.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He's an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.98,0:13:51.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I knew no one would listen to his warnings
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.76,0:13:53.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,and he would come stumbling back to take a stand
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.86,0:13:54.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.22,0:13:58.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,But the one thing I hadn't taken account for was your
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:14:00.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,inexcusable weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.47,0:14:02.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We're not weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:03.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It's just that. . . 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:06.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Who are you to call us weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.13,0:14:08.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What would you say, Captain Kuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.63,0:14:12.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You used to be quite the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.18,0:14:15.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,But face it, Kuro, it's been three years,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.68,0:14:18.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,and we haven't exactly been living the good life
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:19.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,waiting on a rich girl hand and foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:21.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.82,0:14:24.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,For three long years, we've been out sinking pirate ships
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.66,0:14:26.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,and massacring villages.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.53,0:14:29.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:29.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.41,0:14:30.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.09,0:14:32.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You've done nothing this whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.03,0:14:34.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We've been killing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.08,0:14:37.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You butler, there's no way you can beat the Meowban brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.00,0:14:42.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.62,0:14:43.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Butchie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.26,0:14:43.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Siam!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:45.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.02,0:14:52.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You are not Captain anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.44,0:14:55.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,So sorry, but we have to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.33,0:15:08.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.75,0:15:09.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He's behind them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.67,0:15:10.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,How the hell did he. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.21,0:15:12.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'm one of those crazy weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.69,0:15:15.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Who are you going to kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.49,0:15:20.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He snuck up right behind us! Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.96,0:15:27.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:33.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pussyfoot maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.74,0:15:40.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You know, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.35,0:15:48.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I do feel a bit sluggish after all these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.99,0:15:51.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He's handling them like babies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.21,0:15:54.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,And those two nearly defeated Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.25,0:15:59.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,With his pussyfoot maneuver, Captain Kuro could shred
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:02.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,everyone on this beach\Nbefore we drew our next breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:05.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We wouldn't even see it coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.02,0:16:09.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,There is no escape from a killing machine like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.08,0:16:15.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I knew he hadn't grown soft\Nwhen I saw that old habit of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:18.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,That strange way of lifting his glasses
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.26,0:16:19.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,so that he won't cut his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.28,0:16:22.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It's like he never stopped wearing those cat claws.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.06,0:16:24.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,They're almost a part of his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.72,0:16:26.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Of course he hasn't forgotten how to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.53,0:16:36.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You're very lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.67,0:16:38.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'm feeling somewhat merciful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:41.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Maybe these years on dry land have made me soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:45.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'll give you five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:51.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,If you can't deal with the situation here in five
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.84,0:16:55.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,minutes, then I'll kill every last one of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.52,0:17:00.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Now have I made myself clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:08.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:11.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course, that's perfectly clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.49,0:17:13.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Thank you for being so forgiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.21,0:17:16.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,All we have to do is take care of this one guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:18.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.45,0:17:20.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Five minutes will be more than enough time for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.84,0:17:30.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We nearly had him a few minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.78,0:17:33.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We won't need one minute to finish him this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.96,0:17:35.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.30,0:17:36.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.42,0:17:37.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Kill him dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.16,0:17:43.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.16,0:17:46.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.30,0:17:48.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hey, easy there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:49.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You can't just kick them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.89,0:17:50.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Those are my swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.06,0:17:53.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,How about a thanks?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:55.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.77,0:17:58.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:01.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.05,0:18:04.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It won't matter how many swords you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.07,0:18:06.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,And now you'll die holding three of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.93,0:18:09.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:13.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You still don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.09,0:18:22.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,The clock is ticking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.99,0:18:29.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Carrying three swords won't help you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.19,0:18:32.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Unless you know three swords style.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.42,0:18:43.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh no.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:49.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.54,0:19:01.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He took down the Meowban brothers with one attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:15.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:19.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I can promise you everything will be taken care of in
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.79,0:19:21.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,less than five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.37,0:19:36.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:38.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Three minutes left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.01,0:19:47.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'll slaughter him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.11,0:19:51.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Please, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:53.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:54.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hypnotize me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.31,0:19:59.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Just do it, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.24,0:20:01.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.84,0:20:03.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You do sloppy work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:06.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,So he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.19,0:20:08.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I guess all that blubber protected his vitals.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.23,0:20:31.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Butchie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.22,0:20:31.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.22,0:20:38.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.36,0:20:39.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You back for more?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.70,0:20:45.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,This guy knows business.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.99,0:20:48.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He was trouble when he was half this size.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.49,0:20:53.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Then Django had to flip his psycho switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.39,0:21:04.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Now's my chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.23,0:21:07.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I got to wake that lazy jerk up while I still can!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:09.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What is that girl up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.59,0:21:13.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Something tricky, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.39,0:21:15.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Everyone else is busy fighting for their lives
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.47,0:21:16.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,and he's just sleeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.54,0:21:24.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Get up, you bum!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.33,0:21:25.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.32,0:21:27.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.74,0:21:32.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It was nice knowing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.30,0:21:34.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Dodge it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.08,0:21:35.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.51,0:21:38.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.67,0:21:42.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I thought it was just a hypnotic charm,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.69,0:21:44.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,but it's also his weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.59,0:21:48.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami, you cannot just go around stepping on people's
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.11,0:21:49.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.33,0:21:54.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,How is that twerp still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.21,0:21:57.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,That's either the best timing or the worst timing in
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.85,0:21:58.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.77,0:21:59.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I can't tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.97,0:22:04.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.62,0:22:10.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.39,0:22:17.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.00,0:22:19.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,That guy's back in the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.08,0:22:20.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.62,0:22:21.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.76,0:22:23.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Five minutes will never be enough time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.39,0:22:26.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,That hurts, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.96,0:22:27.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Why'd you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.02,0:22:30.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sleeping Beauty, that wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.08,0:22:31.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.76,0:22:36.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.76,0:22:38.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami, did you get hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.36,0:22:39.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Let me see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.04,0:22:41.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.04,0:22:42.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.78,0:22:44.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I've done everything I can for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.35,0:22:47.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,The rest is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.99,0:22:50.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Look, we have to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.39,0:22:51.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We can't afford to lose this fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.91,0:22:52.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.79,0:22:56.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Okay, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.97,0:22:58.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Win this and protect my treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.79,0:23:01.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, the treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.39,0:23:01.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.55,0:23:06.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,One minute and counting.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.32,0:23:09.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Kuro can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.82,0:23:12.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We can't possibly finish them in one minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.48,0:23:13.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Come on, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.46,0:23:15.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Stop messing around and end this already!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.29,0:23:27.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Butchie, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.43,0:23:29.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,There's no more time to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.03,0:23:32.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Kill that three-sword bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.73,0:23:36.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of the freaky, bendable Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.78,0:23:45.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'm coming for you, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.38,0:23:48.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.36,0:23:50.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Why is that shady Butler here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.33,0:23:52.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It's that Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.07,0:23:54.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Didn't he die falling off a cliff?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.53,0:23:58.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nice trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.24,0:24:13.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Don't ever sneak up on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.70,0:24:18.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Unless you want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.15,0:24:19.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Kaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.04,0:24:37.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Usopp 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.28,0:24:41.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Kaya, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.79,0:24:44.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ussop, I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.01,0:24:47.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I don't know how you'll ever forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.91,0:24:49.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.23,0:24:53.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,That Kalahador is a scheming, murdering pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.37,0:24:54.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Never mind that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.91,0:24:55.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.71,0:24:58.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Kaya, your life is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.79,0:25:00.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I told you to run somewhere safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.65,0:25:01.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.33,0:25:02.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You're still here fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.89,0:25:03.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I won't run.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.29,0:25:09.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You fought for me after I treated you so badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.59,0:25:10.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.05,0:25:12.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You're barely alive, but you're still so brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.07,0:25:13.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I just. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.97,0:25:15.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,This is no place for a lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.48,0:25:18.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Madam, please leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.54,0:25:22.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Please, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.88,0:25:23.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Don't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.06,0:25:27.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.86,0:25:29.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Stop this right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.50,0:25:30.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Klahadore!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.90,0:25:38.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I know what you're up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.36,0:25:40.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mary already told me about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.04,0:25:45.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What's the girl from the mansion doing down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.75,0:25:47.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,The whole reason that we're here is to murder that
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.99,0:25:48.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,little rich girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.07,0:25:51.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,If she's here, then we don't have to go to the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.81,0:25:53.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,All we got to do is kill her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.86,0:25:58.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Klahadore, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.40,0:26:00.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,If you want my Fortune, you can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.52,0:26:02.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Take it all and leave this village right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.16,0:26:04.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.43,0:26:07.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I will gladly accept your Fortune, Miss Kaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.17,0:26:08.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.20,0:26:12.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,But I want more.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.46,0:26:14.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You see, simply acquiring wealth isn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.24,0:26:18.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,More than anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.12,0:26:23.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What I want is peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.88,0:26:24.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You want peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.24,0:26:27.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yes, just peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.84,0:26:28.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Peace of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.90,0:26:29.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It's simple, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.94,0:26:33.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I have spent the last three years earning the trust
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.42,0:26:34.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,of the entire village.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.02,0:26:37.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,And to be honest, I find this new sense of peace
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.75,0:26:39.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,and tranquility quite comforting.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.02,0:26:44.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,When my plan comes to fruition, I will live with this
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.23,0:26:45.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,sublime peace of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.79,0:26:55.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.28,0:27:00.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,The glorious comfort of a peaceful life will be mine
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.74,0:27:02.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,for forever and ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.98,0:27:05.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,In short, these pirates are coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.78,0:27:12.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,And you will leave your Fortune to me and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.52,0:27:16.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Miss Kaya, these things will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.95,0:27:19.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,No, you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.77,0:27:21.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You just can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.13,0:27:25.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Run away, Kaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.15,0:27:26.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,There's no use talking to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.67,0:27:28.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Please, get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.53,0:27:31.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You're not Klahador.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.83,0:27:33.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,No, you're not!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.29,0:27:36.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Kaya. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.71,0:27:38.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Leave here right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.35,0:27:39.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Never come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.07,0:27:41.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yes, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.87,0:27:43.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You're all grown up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.35,0:27:45.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,So much has happened in the last three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.97,0:27:48.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Miss Kaya. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.55,0:27:51.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember the things we went through?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.61,0:27:54.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We spent so much time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.35,0:27:58.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Even before your dear sweet parents passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.94,0:28:02.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You we're more than my master.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.52,0:28:03.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You we're my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.36,0:28:06.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,So much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.54,0:28:11.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,So many memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.91,0:28:14.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Together we suffered, and together we rejoiced.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.97,0:28:15.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Like family.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.93,0:28:18.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Klahador ...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.60,0:28:22.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I took you on shopping trips to the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.18,0:28:25.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I looked after you so diligently when you we're ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.44,0:28:29.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,And we used to talk for hours and hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.09,0:28:34.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Kaeya, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.78,0:28:35.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I was devoted to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.86,0:28:37.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,For so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.32,0:28:41.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,For so very long.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.11,0:28:43.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I endured it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.83,0:28:49.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I quietly suffered so that today I could end your
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.37,0:28:52.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,life and take everything that I deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.47,0:29:02.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I, who was once the feared and respected Captain Kuro
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.94,0:29:06.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,had to bow and humble myself before some
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.70,0:29:08.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,snot-nosed little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.94,0:29:11.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It went against every fiber of my being.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.84,0:29:19.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.64,0:29:22.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Can you understand the depth of these daily insults?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.10,0:29:26.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Can you understand the rage created by those
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.78,0:29:28.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,transgressions against my pride?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.32,0:29:46.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Thank you for reminding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.76,0:29:51.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Usopp, I owe you for hitting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.90,0:29:52.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Let's get even.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.52,0:29:54.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.28,0:29:54.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.60,0:29:59.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,If I recall, you hit me as hard as you could, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.53,0:30:00.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.31,0:30:26.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,If he hates getting hit that much, he's about to have
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.39,0:30:27.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,a really bad day!
